Raking in significantly: net income > $5,000,000;
Substantial asset base: total assets > $100,000,000;
Financial overview: includes net income, revenue, assets, liabilities, and equity;
Overall market influence: market capitalization.

sql:
SELECT DISTINCT sector 
FROM companies 
WHERE market_capitalization > 1000000000;

SELECT c.industry, c.sector
FROM companies c
WHERE c.market_capitalization > 10000000000.0;

SELECT companies.company_name, quarterly_reports.date, quarterly_reports.ebit_margin 
FROM companies 
JOIN quarterly_reports ON companies.company_id = quarterly_reports.company_id;
